Package org.lgdcloudsim.interscheduler

Class InterSchedulerResult

java.lang.Object
org.lgdcloudsim.interscheduler.InterSchedulerResult
public class InterSchedulerResult extends Object
The scheduling result of the inter-scheduler. It contains the scheduling result of the instance groups and the failed instance groups. It also contains the outdated user requests which are exceeded the schedule delay limit.
Since:
LGDCloudSim 1.0
Author:
Anonymous

  • Field Details

    • collaborationId

      private int collaborationId
      The collaboration id of the inter-scheduler. It is used for the centralized inter-scheduler of the collaboration zone in CIS.

    • target

      private int target
      The target of the inter-scheduler.

    • isSupportForward

      private Boolean isSupportForward
      Whether the scheduled instance group results support forward again.

    • scheduledResultMap

      private Map<Datacenter,List<InstanceGroup>> scheduledResultMap
      The scheduling result map of the instance groups. For the host-target schedule result, the schedule result has been stored in every instance's Instance.getExpectedScheduleHostId(). TODO needs to be changed from List to Set later to speed up the determination of inclusion.

      target - the target of the inter-scheduler.
